tps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/TaylorSwift-The-Black-Dog-pub-full-capacity-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/TaylorSwift-The-Black-Dog-pub-full-capacity-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/TaylorSwift-The-Black-Dog-pub-full-capacity-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/TaylorSwift-The-Black-Dog-pub-full-capacity-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/TaylorSwift-The-Black-Dog-pub-full-capacity-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>伦敦酒吧“黑狗”因被<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>在她的新专辑中点名后人气上升而被迫“拒绝人们”。</p><p>这位流行歌星在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">《折磨诗人部》</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-tortured-poets-department-album-the-anthology-3619877">扩展版《选集》</a>中的歌曲《黑狗》中提到了这家位于伦敦南部沃克斯豪尔的酒馆。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454"><b>泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）——《受折磨的诗人部》评论：罕见的失误</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>“<em>而你的位置，你忘了关掉它/所以我看着你走进/走进一家叫黑狗的酒吧/在我心里刺穿新的洞</em><em>/你忘了关掉它</em>，”斯威夫特唱道。 “<em>这让我震惊/我只是不明白/你怎么不想我/在《黑狗》中……</em> ”</p><p>这首歌被认为是针对斯威夫特的前男友乔·阿尔文 (Joe Alwyn) 的，他住在酒吧的同一地区（并为 2019 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/you-can-now-take-an-eight-hour-walking-tour-inspired-by-taylor-swifts-london-boy-3588017">《伦敦男孩》</a>提供了灵感）。一些斯威夫特认为《黑狗》可能是关于她去年与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">1975 年</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matty-healy">马蒂·希利</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-matty-healy-seemingly-alludes-to-taylor-swift-split-im-not-really-online-3453109">短暂关系</a>。</p><p> 《折磨的诗人》发行后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hundreds-of-taylor-swift-fans-swarm-london-pub-after-album-shout-out-as-the-black-dog-check-cctv-for-clues-of-ex-3719750">数百名粉丝涌向伦敦的黑狗剧院</a>。酒吧的工作人员表示，他们正在通过搜索闭路电视录像，“拼命地想弄清楚是马蒂还是乔”来过该酒吧。他们还推出了“Swift Half”饮料促销以及新的“Swift Burger”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C5_aD7gobYV/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 54